FBIS3-16284 "drsov050_b_94016" FBIS-SOV-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Media Issues Ministry Cuts Off RTV Video Feed Channels LD1503113594 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 0400 GMT 15 Mar 94 LD1503113594 Moscow Russian Television Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] We have some urgent problems here on Russian TV today. For example, today the Ministry of Communications is cutting us off from all channels of transmission of video material from other cities and countries. Yes, talking on-screen for 20 minutes is not one of the easiest tasks for a newscaster. It seems that Russians will have to do without bright pictures as well as having to do without good-quality bread. Well, that's enough gloomy news; we do have something to boast about: We are the national TV station.
